# my-onramp-project

This is a hand-written AGENTS.md from before anatomy was adopted.

## Rules
- Use camelCase for variables
- Prefer `const` over `let`

## Commands
- `npm test` runs the test suite

## Architecture notes
This is the kind of free-form text users write today that anatomy doesn't
have a structured slot for. After regeneration, the original is preserved
in AGENTS.md.bak so the user can reconcile content manually.
